# Quotation Command - Generate Proposal Presentations

## Overview

Simple command to convert verified proposal templates into professional PowerPoint presentations and PDF documents with viAct branding.

## Usage

```bash
/quotation generate slide <template.md>  # Main command
/quotation status                        # Check current status
/quotation list                          # List recent generations
```

## Commands

### Generate Slides

**Command**: `/quotation generate slide <template.md>`

**Description**: Generate PowerPoint and PDF from a verified proposal template

**Example**:
```bash
/quotation generate slide Leda_Inio_template.md
```

**Output**:
```
