## Error Handling

All errors are shown clearly with actionable messages:

```
❌ Error: Template file not found
   File: nonexistent_template.md
   Solution: Check file path and try again

❌ Error: Template contains placeholders
   Found: 3 placeholders (e.g., [NETWORK_001])
   Solution: Template must be verified first. Remove all [PLACEHOLDER_ID] tags.

❌ Error: PowerPoint generation failed
   File: output.pptx not created
   Solution: Check html2pptx script and validate HTML files

❌ Error: PDF conversion failed
   LibreOffice not found
   Solution: Install LibreOffice: sudo apt install libreoffice
```

